        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-06-13T16:37:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I disagree - ingestion is a boolean operation, did it happen or not.  One of gold\u0027s core assumptions is that a files is not modified after upload.  I only really include the filename to avoid md5 collisions",
